snippet.title: Museum of Other Realities (MOR) - VR Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
An immersive multiplayer art showcase in virtual reality, the Museum of Other Realities is a space to connect, share, and experience a growing collection of mind-bending VR art with others.

Download on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/613900/Museum_of_Other_Realities/

//Music by Zane Alexander
//Trailer by Kert Gartner

Follow the MOR:
https://twitter.com/MuseumOR
https://www.instagram.com/museumofotherrealities/
